data.description: Wonderful two bedroom, two bath home in the heart of Weslaco near entertainment, expressway, restaurants, and schools. As you enter you will notice the details that make this home unique, with soaring ceilings, updated flooring, impressive stone wall with fireplace, and large upstairs loft. Ideal space for gatherings the cozy kitchen is open to the living area and has an island, and quartz countertops upgrade. Bathrooms have been upgraded with quartz countertops, tile flooring, beautiful, tiled shower. Step outside to your large private outdoor space with courtyard. Don't miss out on this gem. Call me today for more information and to schedule your viewing appointment.
